{"tid":2074982,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"笑4 垃圾阿狗又有人中肺炎","createTime":"2020-06-22T13:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T00:56:18.000Z","uid":330582,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2fd509e3065a24734df1a9d084e3ca1db82f888d","tid":2074982,"uid":330582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:36:10.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】阿仙奴禍不單行，於英超重啟2連敗後，一名球員確診新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n《The Athletic》在周一率先爆料，指阿仙奴有一名球員感染了新型冠狀病毒，而且他跟另外兩名球員都有緊密接觸，所以3人都需要隔離7天。雖然報道未有透露這3名球員的名字，但他們都參與了周三以0:3大敗予曼城的英超。 阿仙奴在今次新冠肺炎疫情中可說是非常黑仔，領隊阿迪達在3月已經確診，導致英超暫停了超過100天。 英超在今月復賽，阿迪達康復後親自領軍，可惜兵工廠的表現差強人意，先慘吞藍月3蛋，再在周六聯賽被白禮頓絕殺2:1。更甚的是，中場加列沙卡、中堅柏保路馬里、門將利奴都在比賽中受創，未知需要休息多久。<br />\n<a href=\"http://更多now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9Anow.com&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FwwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=c231f146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">更多now.com</a>體育新聞及英超、西甲精華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43699989176561fda8731f5e388915c78d6ed1a5","tid":2074982,"uid":330582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:38:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=29872059226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fmobileweb%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D29872059226&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FwwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=a7fb78dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=29872059226</a>"},{"pid":"a69519532d61ba09840626e906aa8e1259cd7af7","tid":2074982,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:50:13.000Z","msg":"即係邊三個"},{"pid":"cb065244b680a6c403cd39684f7dcb9fce27cab8","tid":2074982,"uid":37948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:53:40.000Z","msg":"成隊垃圾，30個人中都唔抵可憐"},{"pid":"399df3536e2deea52e05613670e9ad1fcd3ba76d","tid":2074982,"uid":81644,"lik